    <title>Obtaining the software</title>
    <para>
        As of now all Domibus software can be downloaded from the projects<link
            xlink:href="https://secure.e-codex.eu/nexus">
        repository</link>.
        Required credentials will be provided to you by the local person
        responsible for the
        <indexterm>
            <primary>e-CODEX</primary>
        </indexterm>
        e-CODEX or e-SENS
        <indexterm>
            <primary>e-SENS</primary>
        </indexterm>
        project. The artifacts can be directly downloaded from
        <link xlink:href="https://secure.e-codex.eu/nexus/content/groups/public/eu/domibus/domibus/">
            here
        </link>
    </para>
    <note>
        <title>Future planning</title>
        <para>
            It is expected that the final version of Domibus 3 will be hosted on
            <link xlink:href="https://joinup.ec.europa.eu/">joinup</link>
            by the European Commission.
        </para>
    </note>
</section>
